'''Husdent''' (also '''Ho(u)dain''', '''Houdenc''') was a dog owned by [[Tristan]], according to [[Béroul]]'s ''Tristan'' and other versions of the [[Tristan and Iseult]] legend.<ref>{{cite book |title=The Arthurian name dictionary |last=Bruce |first=Christopher W. |authorlink= |year=1999 |publisher=Taylor & Francis |location= |isbn=0-8153-2865-6 |page=271 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XZFbczeMtYcC&pg=PA271 |accessdate=2012-01-04}}</ref>

