{{Infobox person | name = Javier Botet | birth_name = Javier Botet López | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1977|07|30|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Ciudad Real]], [[Spain]] | height = {{height|ft=6|in=6|precision=-1|out=cm}} | occupation = Actor | yearsactive = 2005{{ndash}}present | residence = [[Madrid]]<ref name=boston/> }}
'''Javier Botet López''' (born 30 July 1977) is a Spanish actor.
==Early life== Botet was born in [[Ciudad Real]], the son of Agustín Andrés Botet Rodríguez and María del Carmen Servilia López Nieto.
At age five, he was diagnosed with [[Marfan syndrome]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/how-javier-botets-rare-marfan-syndrome-enabled-his-acting-career-1022027 |title=How Javier Botet's Rare Marfan Syndrome Enabled His Acting Career |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2017-07-20 |accessdate=2017-10-01}}</ref> The [[Hypermobility (joints)|hyperlaxity]] of certain body tissues brought about by Botet's condition has given him extremely long and fine fingers along with a tall, thin build, standing at {{convert|6.6|ft|cm}} tall and weighing {{convert|123|lbs|kg}}.<ref name=boston>{{cite web|last=Feldberg |first=Isaac |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/movies/2017/08/31/meet-javier-botet-boy-scary/TZLMj1UsVVJtEWNTxvwJ8M/story.html |title=Meet Javier Botet, the ‘It’ boy of scary |publisher=The Boston Globe |date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901105022/https://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/movies/2017/08/31/meet-javier-botet-boy-scary/TZLMj1UsVVJtEWNTxvwJ8M/story.html|archive-date=September 1, 2017|accessdate=2017-10-01}}</ref>
==Career== Botet's unique physical traits coupled with an interest in the performing arts led to his first film role in 2005, in [[Brian Yuzna]]'s ''Beneath Still Waters''.<ref name=boston/> Two years later he played the role of [[Tristana Medeiros]] in [[Jaume Balagueró]] and [[Paco Plaza|Paco Plaza's]] 2007 film ''[[REC (film)|REC]]''.<ref name=rec/> Botet has appeared in television and theater roles, including in 2010 as [[Frankenstein's monster]] in Teatros del Canal's stage adaptation of ''[[Frankenstein]]''.<ref>{{cite web |title=Reparto de Actores por Papeles (Cast Actors by Roles): Frankenstein o el moderno Prometeo de Mary Shelley - |url=http://www.teatroscanal.com/espectaculo/1000061000201/ |website=Teatros Del Canal |accessdate=25 July 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725185334/http://www.teatroscanal.com/espectaculo/1000061000201/#tabs1-reparto |archivedate=25 July 2018 |language=es-ES |quote=La Criatura: Javier Botet}}</ref> Botet lives in Madrid.<ref name=boston/>
