r Botet Has a Role in 'Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark' So Get Ready for the Nightmares |url=https://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3520769/javier-botet-mystery-role-scary-stories-tell-dark-get-ready-nightmares/ |website=bloody-disgusting.com |date=10 September 2018}}</ref> |- |colspan=4 style="background-color:#c7dcf6;text-align:center;font-size:100%;"|'''Production crew member''' |- |style="background-color:#efefef;text-align:center;font-size:80%;"|'''Year'''||style="background-color:#efefef;text-align:center;font-size:80%;"|'''Film'''||style="background-color:#efefef;text-align:center;font-size:80%;"|'''Title'''||style="background-color:#efefef;text-align:center;font-size:80%;"|'''Note''' |- |style="text-align:center;"|2017||''[[Alien: Covenant]]''||style="text-align:center;"|<small>Movement Artist (Motion Capture)</small>||style="text-align:center;"|<ref>{{cite film |others=Directed by Ridley Scott. Produced by Ridley Scott, Mark Huffam, Michael Schaefer, David Giler and Walter Hill. Story by Jack Paglen and Michael Green. Screenplay by John Logan and Dante Harper. Director of Photography Dariusz Wolski. Edited by Pietro Scalia. Music by Jed Kurzel.|date=May 19, 2017 |title=Alien: Covenant |title-link=Alien: Covenant |medium= |language= |url=|access-date= |archive-url= |archive-date= |type=Motion picture |location= |publisher=20th Century Fox in association with TSG Entertainment, Brandywine, and Scott Free Productions|id= |isbn= |oclc=1001348614 |quote= |ref=|time=1hr 59min 07sec|time-caption=Botet's screen credit as a production crew-member with the title "Movement Artist (Motion Capture)" occurs at}}</ref> |- |}
